      <title>欧盟考虑对俄罗斯液化天然气项目和转运实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/eu-weighs-sanctions-on-russian-lng-projects-transshipments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟正在与成员国讨论制裁俄罗斯关键液化天然气项目的提案，以及禁止使用欧盟港口再出口运往第三国的供应品的提案，以限制莫斯科从化石燃料中创收的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/eu-weighs-sanctions-on-russian-lng-projects-transshipments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 14:22:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
